sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Source
  participant C as Connector
  participant E as Event Stream
  participant N as Normalizer
  participant D as Data Stores
  participant G as Graph
  participant W as Evidence Workflow
  participant M as Models
  participant P as Policy/Approval
  participant X as Execution

  S->>C: Inventory, events, config, references
  C->>E: Raw canonical envelope
  E->>N: Validate and normalize
  N->>D: Store metadata and references
  N->>G: Project nodes and relationships
  W->>D: Query telemetry and history
  W->>G: Query dependencies and changes
  W->>M: Bounded evidence package
  M->>P: Structured recommendation
  P->>X: Approved action only
  X->>D: Result and verification telemetry
